      • setSegmentedBar

        public boolean setSegmentedBar(SegmentedBar newBar)
        Will through away the existing SegmentedBar to use the given one
        Parameters:
        newBar - the new Segmented bar to be managed by this LabeledBar, Note the Old bar is not destroyed at the conclusion of this function. So do remember to use getSegmentedBar() to clean it up if necessary
        Returns:
        If TRUE, the old SegmentedBar was successfully replaced. otherwise if FALSE, no changes were made
